  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300142515_3_1190-1211",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1190-1211",
      "markText": "长久以来，我觉得恨意是我身上最澎湃的情感。",
      "totalCount": 10386,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300142515&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1190&rangeEnd=1211",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9eb327e0813ab9e2bg015edf?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1190&rangeEnd=1211"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300142515_3_5246-5308",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5246-5308",
      "markText": "这是最后一次尝试。也许我死了比活着更能牵动你的心，至少刚死的那几个星期，在我尸骨未寒之际应是如此，我将在你心里占据一席之地。",
      "totalCount": 8520,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300142515&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5246&rangeEnd=5308",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9eb327e0813ab9e2bg015edf?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5246&rangeEnd=5308"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300142515_4_1833-1906",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1833-1906",
      "markText": "你烦了吗？我很怕让你厌烦。可这封信，请你一字不漏地看完。我可以保证，只拣紧要的事来写。正是这些你不曾了解或者早已忘却的事件，酿就了我们生活的悲剧。",
      "totalCount": 8034,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300142515&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1833&rangeEnd=1906",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9eb327e0813ab9e2bg015edf?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1833&rangeEnd=1906"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300142515_3_1927-2024",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1927-2024",
      "markText": "这世上自然不乏和睦的家庭，但也有无数水火不容的夫妻，他们每日围着同一张桌子吃饭，在同一处盥洗，甚至同床异梦。即便这样也鲜少有人离婚，真是怪事！明明相看两生厌，却还要生活在同一个屋檐下，避无可避…",
      "totalCount": 7497,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300142515&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1927&rangeEnd=2024",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9eb327e0813ab9e2bg015edf?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1927&rangeEnd=2024"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300142515_4_3669-3737",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3669-3737",
      "markText": "她们越是厌恶我，我就越变本加厉地展露自己的丑恶。我的青春不过是一场悠长的自杀。为了遮掩不讨喜的天性，我便迫不及待地刻意做些令人生厌的事。",
      "totalCount": 6944,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300142515&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3669&rangeEnd=3737",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9eb327e0813ab9e2bg015edf?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3669&rangeEnd=3737"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300142515_6_3614-3680",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3614-3680",
      "markText": "这样可怕的想法令我毛骨悚然。我思忖：全都是假的……她在骗我。我并未得到救赎。我何来的自信觉得有个少女会爱上我呢？我是个没人爱的人啊！",
      "totalCount": 6876,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300142515&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3614&rangeEnd=3680",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9eb327e0813ab9e2bg015edf?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3614&rangeEnd=3680"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300142515_7_1255-1310",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1255-1310",
      "markText": "接下来的几年里，你就在接二连三的怀胎、出岔和分娩中度过。这也让我有了疏远你的充分借口。我暗中堕入了放荡的生活。",
      "totalCount": 6810,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300142515&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1255&rangeEnd=1310",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9eb327e0813ab9e2bg015edf?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1255&rangeEnd=1310"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300142515_3_2144-2177",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2144-2177",
      "markText": "这些年来，我从未送你任何形式的生日礼物，并非我忘了，只是为了报复。",
      "totalCount": 6494,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300142515&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2144&rangeEnd=2177",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9eb327e0813ab9e2bg015edf?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2144&rangeEnd=2177"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300142515_3_1668-1718",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1668-1718",
      "markText": "我的一生在牺牲中度过，这些回忆侵蚀着我。经年累月之下，心中的怨怼早已破土而出，成了一株遮天蔽日的树。",
      "totalCount": 6344,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300142515&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1668&rangeEnd=1718",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9eb327e0813ab9e2bg015edf?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1668&rangeEnd=1718"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300142515_9_3774-3852",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "3774-3852",
      "markText": "尤其……一旦分居，我就得退还你嫁妆中苏伊士运河公司的股权，可我早已习惯将它们当作私产。一想到得放弃这些股权，我就坐立难安（还没算上你父亲给我们的年金……）。",
      "totalCount": 5720,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300142515&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3774&rangeEnd=3852",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9eb327e0813ab9e2bg015edf?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=3774&rangeEnd=3852"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300142515_3_4673-4724",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4673-4724",
      "markText": "即便我们最紧密结合的时刻，他也要横插一脚，如影随形。那一晚，你叫了他的名字，还记得吗？可你仍不餍足……",
